3?" }{TEXT -1 2 "  " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 152 "****We needed to \+
include the x in the solve command, because if we don't specify what t
o solve for, Maple chooses for us.  In this case it solved for c." }}
{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 107 "Use the \+
solve command replacing x with a, b, c respectively.  You should be ab
le to anticipate the results." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}
{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 14 "solve(p3=0,a);" }}{PARA 11 "
" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#,$*&,&*&%\"bG\"\"\"%\"xGF(F(%\"cGF(F(F)!\"#!\"\"
" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 14 "solve(p3=0,b);" }}
